Lineage: Webcast -> AdobeHDS script -> .flv -> mkvmerge GUI-> .mkv (no transcoding)
Video: MPEG4 Video (H264) 1280x720 2400 Kbps 29.97 fps
Audio: AAC 128 Kbps 44.1 KHz stereo 

Lucinda Williams' new 14-song set, 'The Ghosts of Highway 20', is a road album of a sort,as well as a remarkable distillation of her writerly gifts. She grapples with mortality on a stark, emotionally raw alt-country masterpiece. She visited KCRW to share some ofher new material in an intimate live setting.
